data.description: Welcome to your private SW Washington retreat hidden away above the Columbia River. This serene hideaway is close to the cultural amenities of nearby Kelso and Longview downtowns, while simultaneously being private, secure, and serene. Enjoy expansive views and greenery, and ample room to wander, rest, and roost with chicken coop, garden space, and plenty of room for toys across two full acres. One edge of the property overlooks a cemetery, so the neighbors are very, very quiet (and will never move). Kelso is known for excellent schools and small-town feel, and is less than an hour from the PDX metropolitan area. Come tour and see why this hidden gem is exactly what you're looking for!
